erm 同exam 後都會元氣大傷 好累"},{"pid":"f0b736e0af537d9c1d0673bc996ceff48f0466b9","tid":684616,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"49dbfcd7ef70c3f58d22e52928df5333ce908e2e","tid":684616,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5ddf59daa885e53c6f7d0e8bedba7bcfc19707e","tid":684616,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee5b55cc4c9df1abc9e99ad3e0c38daad425720b","tid":684616,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:25:35.000Z","msg":"我主要用來背vocab<br />\nIt's very good<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:32:41.000Z","msg":"總之你有咩想背就整張卡片save入個軟件<br />\n然後個軟件就會根據遺忘曲線定時定候check返你仲記唔記得<br />\n幫你將短期記憶變成長期記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過佢主要用途係幫你喺幾個禮拜甚至幾個月後仲記得d嘢<br />\n如果係中學雞想用嚟準備嚟緊6月考試咁就幫助不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad25b52e20677612de66ddf16d0abe743b92542","tid":684616,"uid":129030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:12:47.000Z","msg":"唔好背單字，用iPad, iPhone iBook app download epub 版英文書睇，唔識既字highlight 住即刻睇meaning, 唔使刻意記住，明左意思唔阻住理解就繼續<br />\n<br />\n睇完本書，由頭開始，睇一次highlight 左字果句，睇下仲記唔記得，唔記得就用notes app 記低<br />\n<br />\n之後繼續睇第二本書，得閒可以複雜啲字，記得意思就delete 左佢，唔記得去返本書highlight 果度睇返果句，成句連字理解"},{"pid":"bebb7c4e84a1d9a470398506ea4430c9abcd325b","tid":684616,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"1. 先將啲句子嘅第一隻字抽出嚟做Index<br />\n然後成句睇一次，理解佢講緊乜，英文差嘅可以將句野轉返做中文睇完再背英文<br />\n<br />\n2. 溫完一個Ch.就瞓一兩粒鐘，5個Ch.就瞓足4次<br />\n<br />\n3. 考試測驗前一定要夠瞓"},{"pid":"aa2ddb4572a31d6022fc8f028d143c2f528c02aa","tid":684616,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fddea9d84d623873c69979e392d026444290cd52","tid":684616,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"531bd8bbde2b2ca50076da6226ee63ef03bd82bb","tid":684616,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa2ddb4572a31d6022fc8f028d143c2f528c02aa","tid":684616,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:58:11.000Z","msg":"你唔咁做，當你想拎返背咗嘅野出嚟，咁咪要由頭背起<br />\n當然如果你冇呢個問題嘅話係OK嘅<br />\n因為好多時唔係嗰個人背唔到，係佢背完拎唔返出嚟"}]}